improved_metadata.title: Call Me Mrs. Sprayfoam: Insulation Parody
improved_metadata.description: A comedic parody song that twists Carly Rae Jepsen's 'Call Me Maybe' into an advertisement for spray foam insulation services. It's a lighthearted take on home improvement.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: It looks like you need insulation, maybe, so here's my number, call the phone, lady.
